narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned a lot about how to individualize my writing process. We talked about a ton of strategies which helped me significantly with longer form research papers. Additionally, I learned about effective reading strategies and topics including fragmentation.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: All the time we spent in class talking about writing process got a bit redundant.
The time frame of this course is super manageable, and I loved the pacing. That being said, I wish we could've had more in class time for peer feedback and discussion.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes absolutely. It provided a really strong foundation for college level writing and time management. The skills I nurtured in this class helped me more easily complete complex papers in other classes.
